USDA-sunFeb18.ipynb outlines the way that the content-based recommender system #foodgoals was built.
#foodgoals allows users to query any product in the database and find a version that is more nutritionally aligned with their goals.

Datasets were pulled from the USDA's branded food products database
https://www.ars.usda.gov/northeast-area/beltsville-md-bhnrc/beltsville-human-nutrition-research-center/nutrient-data-laboratory/docs/usda-branded-food-products-database/ 


More info on #food goals: http://wrightdatasolutions.com/about 
